ejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这张专辑是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯</a>（Harry Styles）“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-new-album-harrys-house-3226209">哈利之家”（Harry&#39;s House</a> ）以来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fenders-people-watching-earns-biggest-uk-opening-week-for-british-act-since-harry-styles-harrys-house-3842384">的英国最大开幕周</a>。这也标志着他有史以来最大的开幕周，售出的单位比2019年的首张“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">Hypersonic导弹</a>”和2021年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">十七岁</a>”合计。</p><p>他只加入了其他八位艺术家，这些艺术家在这个十年的一周中销售了100,000张英国专辑的销售 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">柯利</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">拿走那个</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">阿巴</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">北极猴子</a>。 “观看者”也已成为本世纪英国表演最快的乙烯基专辑。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对“观看者”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">四星级评论</a>中写道：“反思性，分析性和脆弱性，“观看的人”确实做了标题可能所暗示的：盘点使Fender成为他今天的人的角色，朋友和亲人。当他回顾迄今为止的生活时，他以敏感的方式接近每条曲目，甚至有罪恶感，也要考虑下一个可能是谁。”</p><p>在其他山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）新闻中，这位音乐家最近嘲笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-continues-to-tease-another-new-album-says-hes-desperate-to-make-a-punk-album-3840765">另一张新专辑，他说他“拼命”倾向于朋克风格的声音</a>。</p><p>在最近关于Apple Music 1的<em>The Zane Lowe节目</em>的采访中，Geordie词曲作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-planning-next-album-ive-got-a-load-of-new-songs-already-3839928">开放了有关与毒品战争的亚当·格兰迪尔（Adam Granduciel）合作的工作，并重申他已经在进行了后续工作</a>。</p><p> Fender最近在夏季<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-huge-summer-2025-uk-stadium-shows-buy-tickets-3814931">即将举行的英国体育场巡回演出</a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">增加了日期</a>- 包括曼彻斯特的Wythenshawe Park，Edinburgh Summer Sessions和贝尔法斯特的Boucher Road竞争地。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsam-fender-tickets%2Fartist%2F5242347" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">在此处</a>找到英国巡回演出的清单。</p><p>邮报山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）表演，并在2025年<a href="https://www.nme.com">英国</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sam-fender-perform-and-give-shout-out-to-newcastle-and-north-shields-at-the-brit-awards-2025-3842681">大奖上向纽卡斯尔（Newcastle）和北盾（North Shields）大喊大叫</a>。</p> ;
